text: Best Cai Peng in Bukit Batok! Every selection, be it meat or vegetable, is nice! As you can see, I am a clear fan of their fried mid joint chicken wings hahaha

Cheap & good!

Being a Nasi Lemak cum Chinese Rice stall, their dishes naturally includes lots of deep fried stuffs which I am a fan of. Even during lunch hours, you'll see long queues with numerous old folks lining up which speaks volumes of their popularity.
